* Require glib-2.0 >= 2.79.2
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)


2.78.1 (stable):

Glib:
* Dispatcher: Allow destroy during emit
  (Kjell Ahlstedt) Issue #116 (PBS)

gmmproc:
* h2def.py: Make return types that are unsigned work.
  Required by gtkmm4, GdkDmabufTextureBuilder
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)

