* Require glib-2.0 >= 2.71.2
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)
* MSVC build: Support VS2022 builds
  (Chun-wei Fan)
* Meson build: Specify 'check' option in run_command()
  Require Meson >= 0.55.0
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)


