  (Kjell Ahlstedt)
* MemoryOutputStream, UnixOutputStream: Implement PollableOutputStream.
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)
* TlsDatabase: create_certificate_handle_vfunc():
  Fix memory leak, and correctly return nulltpr.
  (Kjell Ahlstedt) Bug #783360

