* Use std::memset() instead of GLIBMM_INITIALIZE_STRUCT
  (Because it causes compiler warnings with --std=c++ with g++,
  because that defines __STRICT_ANSI__.) and deprecate
  GLIBMM_INITIALIZE_STRUCT.
  (Kjell Ahlstedt)

