  (Kjell Ahlstedt)

2.32.0 (stable):

Glib:
* Dispatcher: Don't send messages to a deleted Dispatcher.
  (Kjell Ahlstedt) Bug #651942
* Make SignalTimeout/SignalIdle::connect_once() more thread safe.
  (Kjell Ahlstedt) Suggested by Chris Vine. Bug #396963
